(after the HEADER_P rule):

            | HEADER_P MATCH
                {
                    $$ = makeDefElem("header", (Node *) makeString("match"), @1);
                }

This should be inserted between the existing HEADER_P rule (lines 3495-3498) and
the QUOTE opt_as Sconst rule (lines 3499-3502).

